---
title: Sweet Chili Tofu & Green Bean Bowls with Crispy Fried Onions & Cilantro
description: Good news, friends: The path to sweet-and-savory dinner bliss is only 20 minutes away! In this recipe, turkey and green beans are coated in a sumptuous sweet chili sauce, then topped with fresh cilantro and crispy fried onions. Everything comes together over a bed of fluffy rice. The results? A symphony of flavors and textures so delicious, you might just lick the bowl.
